      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay so it's all very professional and regulated, but it still feels a bit weird to just hand over a huge amount of money to a stranger or a company and just hope they don't do anything shady with it. is there anything else i should look out for during the closing phase to make sure no one is trying to steal from the pot? like are there any hidden traps or things that could trip me up?",
